yet another good set complete with the original intro song put back in with the only exception is that the door clank happens after Katie Sagal is on the intro, which makes it truly funny, the 2 season set finally has the actual seasons labeled this time so you can tell which season is which and all the favorite episodes are here in this season set, still same issues plague this set from the last 2 sets and the remaining sets a quick recap on that is all 4 discs are on one spindle and you should just save yourself time and buy a 4 disc box replacement to save the discs and make them look better, all in all a better price for 2 seasons and to remind anyone its not a remaster or remake just the original set squashed 2 discs per season so basically 14 episodes on 1 disc with the correct song in it, plus much nicer on shelves to go with other dvd or blu ray sets
